org.mixare.localMarker

Class ImageMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mixare.localMarker.LocalMarker
      • org.mixare.localMarker.ImageMarker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Marker>, Marker

    public class ImageMarker
extends LocalMarker
    Local Image Marker that handles drawing images locally (extents LocalMarker) Note: LinkURL is the url when marker is clicked on. Note: ImageURL is the url that links to solid image.
    Author:
    DevBinnooh , A.Egal
